eletonState extends State<MatchListPageSkeleton> {\n  MatchListPageStatus _statu
s = MatchListPageStatus.loading;\n  List<MockMatchItem> _matches = [];\n  // ...
纯 UI 状态，无 BLoC、无 Repository、无 Dio\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. 需更新文档\n\
